### UPDATE TRACKING UPDATE
PATCH http://app.xycargo.com/v1/shipment-tracking-updates/1 HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "location": "Accra Airport - Gate A12",
    "notes": "Package loaded onto flight AA123, departing at 15:30"
}

### RESPONSE

{
  "status": "success",
  "code": 200,
  "tracking_update": {
    "update_id": 1,
    "shipment_id": 1,
    "status": "in_transit",
    "location": "Accra Airport - Gate A12",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-21 14:00:00",
    "notes": "Package loaded onto flight AA123, departing at 15:30"
  },
  "message": "Tracking update updated successfully"
}

